@valdres/search-languages

This package vendors generated and curated content from two upstream
projects. Run `bun run build:stemmers` and `bun run build:stopwords` to
regenerate from source.

---

Snowball stemmers (src/stemmers/*.ts)

Generated from the Snowball algorithm source files at
https://github.com/snowballstem/snowball, pinned to v3.0.1, using the
Snowball compiler's `-js` target. Languages: arabic, armenian, danish,
dutch, english, finnish, french, german, greek, hindi, hungarian,
indonesian, irish, italian, lithuanian, nepali, norwegian, portuguese,
romanian, russian, serbian, spanish, swedish, tamil, turkish.

Per-language splitter regexes were derived from Orama's SPLITTERS table
(Apache-2.0, https://github.com/oramasearch/orama).

